Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,較計劃提前4天剿滅敵軍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收兵返城 召集賽爾貝莉亞等人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎 沃塞爾橋的作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.29,0:02:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓正規軍啞口無言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧那場勝利 情勢正趨於好轉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.89,0:02:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍也不得不對我們刮目相看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.18,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.98,0:02:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 有心事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:35.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 談不上心事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被我說中了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇奪沃塞爾橋的年輕小隊長閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.15,0:02:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛路上也免不了心煩事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 又不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 你的副官是個女孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得叫艾麗西婭什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她處得怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過得去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.44,0:03:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是別人家的飯香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.55,0:03:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第一小隊雖猛將如雲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎奈缺少鮮花點綴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 襯衣全部拿去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話穿我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎 不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊…隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種場合敬禮就免了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的部下？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 走吧維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安終於起駕回城
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.81,0:04:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好事一樁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有心情高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沃塞爾橋落入加利亞的狗崽子手裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守軍到底在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.59,0:04:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 稍安勿躁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實令人驚訝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是他們讓坦克渡河的戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人也喜歡做些別出心裁的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出心裁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終究是外行人的異想天開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.07,0:04:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手可是卑賤的民兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.81,0:04:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然一敗塗地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓皇帝陛下顏面無存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.58,0:04:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠身份貴賤就能贏下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭也會輕鬆許多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是討論這種事的場合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是 加利亞軍欲以這次小小的反抗為契機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始轉守為攻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.07,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須早除後患
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在加利亞軍的反攻未成氣候前 扼殺於萌芽中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 為打壓加利亞軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,須對反攻勢頭最猛的中部戰線增兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.47,0:05:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此需要鞏固加利亞南部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自克羅汀的補給線路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷戈爾 率部以克羅汀為據點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮重整中部戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.38,0:05:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶格爾負責支援格雷戈爾後方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並保護補給道路暢通
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.48,0:05:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽爾貝莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.59,0:05:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾欲前往巴裡亞斯沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨駕同行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.81,0:05:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願為殿下肝腦塗地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發 將加利亞的嫩芽從大地上剷除
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達蒙將軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談什麼知不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說吧 如果我們是草原上的野兔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是狐狸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天敵？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達蒙是貴族出身的正規軍高官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官威顯赫 為一己私慾不放過任何獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂老奸巨猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.84,0:06:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說不把義勇軍當成友軍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.96,0:06:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是不屑一顧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 狐狸不是這麼壞的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 和他相提並論是侮辱狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達蒙他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第七小隊可能要去支援達蒙麾下的部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉打攪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.77,0:06:57.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.20,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 有什麼需要道歉的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這個 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.26,0:07:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰神阿瑞斯被阿弗洛狄忒女神們看到赤身裸體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會感覺受到羞辱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說白了 就算被你看到赤膊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.07,0:07:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.17,0:07:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是隊長的副官吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.52,0:07:38.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為管好手下的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.44,0:07:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在看慣了比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金 你也說幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快讓他把衣服穿起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.68,0:07:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個問題啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 蘭扎特小隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我法爾迪奧就好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.51,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧小隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人 絕對是樂在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎 艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.93,0:08:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍的達蒙將軍請你去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達蒙將軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義勇軍 第七小隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金·鞏特爾少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.11,0:08:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同隊副官 艾麗西婭·梅爾姬沃特中士
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你就是鞏特爾將軍家的公子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召你們來不為其他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.14,0:08:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有關克羅汀攻略戰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我加利亞正規軍 正計劃在中部戰線發起反攻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰役的關鍵就在於克羅汀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝國軍中部戰線的根本之所在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其補給基地就坐落在這片森林中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.15,0:09:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片森林裡有這麼重要的設施…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.11,0:09:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片森林？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去過？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 大學的課外研修時去過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座補給基地 是帝國軍中部戰線的生命線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如能截斷其補給線路 優勢必將倒向於我軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這次作戰你們不必隨行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.01,0:09:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此重要的作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們只會拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果願意當我們的擋箭牌 當然可以重新考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…我們靠一己之力奪回了沃塞爾橋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不會拖大隊的後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.53,0:09:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼傻話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.13,0:09:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是運氣好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.36,0:09:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個臭長官
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.46,0:09:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金也不回他幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人沒指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本心不在焉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這麼想參加的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓中士單獨加入正規軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不必了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我們不參加本次作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 艾麗西婭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.79,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金 就甘心被人這麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.58,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.78,0:10:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個臭老頭不停地在挖苦你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用色迷迷的眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意當面通知人家被排除在外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不說回他幾句？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.30,0:10:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 注意看房間牆上了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為炫耀自己 掛滿了動物毛皮和裝飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是做不到他那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.92,0:11:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他既然不需要我們 何必同流合污呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們時刻整裝待發就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭迎駕到 格雷戈爾將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.14,0:11:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲拉魯德能迎來人稱帝國惡魔的將軍閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南部戰線的勝利也指日可待…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.51,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡要匯報戰況
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.14,0:11:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前線兵力勢均力敵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,局部與加利亞軍有小規模交火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不會對兩軍大勢產生影響
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯獨有一件事令人在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.95,0:11:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有情報稱加利亞正規軍的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.32,0:11:59.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達蒙將軍欲率一支中隊偷襲這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何應對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必多慮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許參加作戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把我們視為戰鬥力？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.65,0:12:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 正規軍那群傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我不去說他們幾句
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想發號施令？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不是說好聽我指揮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.24,0:12:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就甘心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.64,0:12:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也並非好戰成性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能被這樣瞧不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算來硬的 也得讓他們見識我們的厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令嗎 看來一句怨言不敢說就回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會被人看不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.53,0:13:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如趁此機會打掃宿舍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 吃你不消
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始 克羅汀森林補給基地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突襲作戰正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍進發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格雷戈爾將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞軍自基地西南方向這裡挺進
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.51,0:13:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先讓誘敵部隊上前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人必會上鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一鼓作氣擊之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那支部隊會損失慘重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可避免
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為把加利亞那群傢伙斬盡殺絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須不擇手段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.95,0:14:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.99,0:14:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們為與帝國作對 追悔莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是上次的演習報告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.55,0:14:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請過目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去把這些晾起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.56,0:14:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇茜看著正在洗的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在我桌上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.75,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾金這人莫名其妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家又各管各的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後可能跟不上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟不上誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.84,0:14:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.22,0:14:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.17,0:15:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和維爾金 貌似都正值煩惱多多的季節啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話 可以跟我商量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.18,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.96,0:15:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.04,0:15:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人到底什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在想維爾金的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這人沒準脾氣 又不知在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完完全全是個自行其是的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被將軍挖苦時也樂呵呵的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.80,0:15:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想著團結部下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.11,0:15:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是變化無常 渾然天成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名其妙 自行其是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我們跟著忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.01,0:16:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 感覺能夠依賴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.18,0:16:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所說 他這人難以捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 也並非全是弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奪回沃塞爾橋時也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個該出手時就出手的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次見他這種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.47,0:16:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之現在給他一點信任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是他的副官
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.65,0:16:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這等事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.28,0:17:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加利亞軍65%的兵力遭到毀滅性打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們已開始敗退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也暫且撤回傷員 重整戰力為好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.09,0:17:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人丟盔卸甲時 怎能鳴金收兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 士兵這樣下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能為皇帝陛下吃苦受累的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必在我軍中呆下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須讓他們知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咬傷獅子的野狗會有什麼下場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 被稱為帝國惡魔的鐵血軍人格雷戈爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直無血無淚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不許擅離職守
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.29,0:17:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我重整隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.37,0:17:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍損失已過七成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法再繼續戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認我撤離後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即向全軍發出撤退命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 想方設法堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身家性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.34,0:18:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交換俘虜時 我們會動用他們的幹部級別將領
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.56,0:18:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.22,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.81,0:18:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥到最後一兵一卒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.07,0:18:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 只有達蒙將軍僥倖逃生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍完敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拒絕了第七小隊參戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從結果來看成了件善舉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 司令部已經下令義勇軍攻打克羅汀森林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:19:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們第七小隊 被賦予打頭陣的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉強了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小隊明晨出發前往克羅汀森林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.93,0:19:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠理解大家的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍 而且是達蒙將軍率領的部隊被擊退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠我們這些義勇軍能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.99,0:19:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如之前所說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們全力爭取生還
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果不贊同這次作戰 請直說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須服從隊長的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.06,0:19:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是隊長的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 這是讓正規軍刮目相看的好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:20:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去 我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.80,0:20:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.09,0:20:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算上我們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經帕羅特中隊長許可 我們將前往支援你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 法爾迪奧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.56,0:20:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你們獨出風頭的 維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.49,0:20:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油干
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 確實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.43,0:20:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不知不覺就被他帶動了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.53,0:20:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.71,0:20:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個該出手時就出手的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:57.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我對你有點刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刮目相看？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.87,0:21:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還說什麼見外話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿瑞斯以裸身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿弗洛狄忒以裹身之物相示之
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.57,0:21:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經是互相看過裸體與內衣的關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裸體和…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.64,0:21:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 維爾金
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.39,0:21:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是法爾迪奧他…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======ED=======
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:45.83,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.84,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.78,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}思い出は僕を　海辺に導く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:22:00.67,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.95,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心地良さばかりを　求めて生きていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.44,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}ぐるぐる同じ場所で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:25.18,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}そんな僕の前に　現れた笑顔は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:28.91,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太陽のようだった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:37.37,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}君に会いたくて　夜明けも待たずに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:41.48,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}走り出していた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:47.14,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}笑い合えるように　唄い合えるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:52.25,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}今もう一度飛んでみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:56.13,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}あの風にのって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:45.83,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想見你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.21,0:21:49.84,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飛奔出門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:55.78,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}回憶將我 引向海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.07,0:22:00.67,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:04.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘風飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.80,0:22:15.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}一味追求安逸的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:19.44,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}原地踏步不前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:25.18,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}出現在我面前的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:28.91,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}像太陽般燦爛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:37.37,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}太想見你 不等天明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.67,0:22:41.48,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}就飛奔出門
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:47.14,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}想和你共同歡笑歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.45,0:22:52.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻真想再次飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:56.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}乘風飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,oped,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,=======NEXT=======
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.92,0:23:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 我叫蘇茜·埃文斯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.63,0:23:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父親的強力推薦下 雖然加入義勇軍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥和組織生活並不是我專長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 為了不給埃文斯家族抹黑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.51,0:23:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會加倍努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 戰場女武神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.97,0:23:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五章 克羅汀奇襲戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.11,0:23:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃文斯的家訓是勇氣與誠實
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.93,0:23:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇茜·埃文斯 出發
